@startuml
title Hình 4.7 - Sơ đồ luồng sự kiện Kafka giữa các dịch vụ

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam ArrowColor #475569
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.2
skinparam ComponentBorderColor #475569
skinparam ComponentBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam QueueBorderColor #475569
skinparam QueueBackgroundColor #FEF3C7

left to right direction

component "identity-service" as Identity #DBEAFE
component "user-service" as User
component "product-service" as Product #DCFCE7
component "search-service" as Search
component "order-service\nSaga Orchestrator" as Order #FEF3C7
component "inventory-service" as Inventory
component "payment-service" as Payment
component "voucher-service" as Voucher
component "notification-service" as Notification
component "flash-sale-service" as FlashSale #FEE2E2
queue "Kafka KRaft\n13 topics" as Kafka

Identity --> Kafka : user-registered
Kafka --> User : create profile

Product --> Kafka : product-created\nproduct-updated\nproduct-deleted
Kafka --> Search : update Elasticsearch index

Order --> Kafka : order-created
Kafka --> Inventory : reserve stock
Inventory --> Kafka : inventory-updated\ninventory-failed
Kafka --> Order : update saga state

Order --> Kafka : payment-requested
Kafka --> Payment : process COD/payment
Payment --> Kafka : payment-success\npayment-failed
Kafka --> Order : confirm/cancel order

Order --> Kafka : order-confirmed
Kafka --> Inventory : confirm reservation
Kafka --> Notification : send confirmation email

Order --> Kafka : order-cancelled
Kafka --> Inventory : release reservation
Kafka --> Voucher : release voucher
Kafka --> Notification : send cancellation email

FlashSale --> Kafka : flash-sale-order-requested\n3 partitions
Kafka --> Order : create flash sale order

note bottom
  Kafka tách các tác động phụ và luồng Saga khỏi request đồng bộ.
  Các consumer xử lý idempotent để chống duplicate do at-least-once delivery.
end note

@enduml
